headline: Are Wall Street Analysts Bullish on Clorox Stock?

headline: Clorox’s Q4 Earnings Call: Our Top 5 Analyst Questions
summary: Clorox’s fourth quarter results were met with a negative market reaction, as flat year-on-year sales masked underlying challenges in profitability and margins.
